Northwestern
University
(
NU
)
is
a
private
research
university
in
Evanston
,
Illinois
,
United
States.
Established
in
1851
to
serve
the
historic
Northwest
Territory
,
it
is
the
oldest
chartered
university
in
Illinois.
The
university
has
its
main
campus
along
the
shores
of
Lake
Michigan
in
the
Chicago
metropolitan
area
.
